column5: Oh they'll eat!!! Just pray they are not social distancing from your hook!!!!!   😁
They’re didn’t for me today they were really keeping their distance
i just hit that ugly season up at my place that the ice is no longer safe enough to get where i need to go to fish...last week was good...really good though. Now i patiently wait.
Now you know why I tell you to fish way over there,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,   LMAO  Yes I am jealous now,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
I'm hoping that I don't end up in this situation with daytime temps in the pluses as far as I can see. Good thing is there's still 2ft. of ice for now.
